      "line": 46,
      "message": "Heads up that we are dealing with inconsistencies in service naming.  Some charts are using common.fullname and some are not.  The way we are leaning it to use common.fullname which will prefix the service name with the Release.Name.\nSo the K8s DNS entry here for these apps isn't really sdc-be.namespace anymore it should be [releasename]-sdc-be.[namespace].  \nWe will merge this as is and next week take another pass to line up service naming.",
